## Return information

**RESP2:**

[Integer reply](../../develop/reference/protocol-spec#integers): the number of fields that were removed from the hash, excluding any specified but non-existing fields.

**RESP3:**

[Integer reply](../../develop/reference/protocol-spec#integers): The number of fields that were removed from the hash, excluding any specified but non-existing fields.

